            Our research spans multiple areas at the intersection of artificial intelligence, machine learning, 
            and systems engineering. We focus on both theoretical foundations and practical applications 
            that address real-world challenges.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">

      <!-- Research Areas -->
